{"tid":2308084,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美擬制裁中芯國際、中海油","createTime":"2020-12-01T15:13:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-01T20:16:56.000Z","uid":25558,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"894d1f2807724e8d595fc2889e9e33b06da6ad6c","tid":2308084,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T15:13:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20201201/D32XOCICAZESRFBVPPZTGDLEAE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20201201%2FD32XOCICAZESRFBVPPZTGDLEAE%2F&d=TN93oS71akEChVkkxtef2dB4iDtRAy51VXy1YCRVmoY%3D&h=d89895a2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20201201%2FD32XOCICAZESRFBVPPZTGDLEAE%2F&h=5a5856b3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20201201/D32XOCICAZESRFBVPPZTGDLEAE/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n美擬制裁中芯國際、中海油<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/q9og-2jemztOnvWNTFgti_bDDgY=/1329x886/filters:quality\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fq9og-2jemztOnvWNTFgti_bDDgY%3D%2F1329x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality&d=TN93oS71akEChVkkxtef2dB4iDtRAy51VXy1YCRVmoY%3D&h=df56556f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fq9og-2jemztOnvWNTFgti_bDDgY%3D%2F1329x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality&h=749bc23d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/q9og-2jemztOnvWNTFgti_bDDgY=/1329x886/filters:quality</a>(100)/<a href=\"http://cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/R4M3LHWNINFSJHOUZVRA6UMN24.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FR4M3LHWNINFSJHOUZVRA6UMN24.jpg&d=TN93oS71akEChVkkxtef2dB4iDtRAy51VXy1YCRVmoY%3D&h=3d5dab21\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/R4M3LHWNINFSJHOUZVRA6UMN24.jpg</a><br />\n■美擬新增中芯國際入制裁黑名單。<br />\n<br />\n上周有傳美國特朗普政府，將新增四間被指與解放軍有關聯的中國企業到國防部制裁名單，有關企業包括在港上市的中芯國際（0981）和中海油（0883）的母公司中國海洋石油集團。若措施落實，美國投資者將再不能購買這些企業股票。中國外交部表示，希望美方不要為中美間正常交流合作設置壁壘。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n受影響華企增至35間<br />\n<br />\n路透社上月披露，美國國防部擬再新增四間中國企業到黑名單，使受影響的中國企業增至35間。特朗普最近發佈行政命令，將禁止美國投資者從明年11月起購買黑名單上企業的股票。路透社前日再引述消息，指最新上榜的四間企業，包括內地規模最大的芯片企業中芯國際，目前同時在紐約和香港上市的中海油，以及中國建設科技集團和中國國際工程諮詢有限公司。<br />\n<br />\n去年5月從紐約交易所退市的。。。。。。。。。。。。。重大打擊，因其範圍有限。拜登新政府的立場存在不確定性，而且美國基金的持倉已經很少。<br />\n<br />\n路透社"},{"pid":"53c12c343ee810dce3b3a33804e98a1f748e2d24","tid":2308084,"uid":5178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T15:39:30.000Z","msg":"驚閪咩<br />\n祖國咁強大<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4812fdcf048ded21aa58a918df662aeec9fa528","tid":2308084,"uid":66049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T15:41:36.000Z","msg":"等多個月拜登就會解除制裁"},{"pid":"d86005b037abe79d71ffc8e3de5b239f0b906a21","tid":2308084,"uid":296600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T17:46:48.000Z","msg":"根本所有中資都有問題<br />\n唔係偷技術就洗黑錢走資呃綠咭乜乜柒柒<br />\n應該一次過ban晒再逐間審查先畀佢哋入美國市場"},{"pid":"bbcd4d988eb980da901916095e7bbec0cbdb83ae","tid":2308084,"uid":286792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T18:14:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"36c77bb463d0555c042e3a18fb14c113b6619069","tid":2308084,"uid":91813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T18:15:29.000Z","msg":"今日見到個新聞put左半倉<br />\n等收錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3191c52136fe5dd4aa6cf8b5374350da9d5dec1c","tid":2308084,"uid":76848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"53c12c343ee810dce3b3a33804e98a1f748e2d24","tid":2308084,"uid":5178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T15:39:30.000Z","msg":"驚閪咩<br />\n祖國咁強大<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T20:16:56.000Z","msg":"驚閪咩<br />\n(